      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 1991 Acura NSX, a masterclass in analog engineering. This specimen features the high-revving 3.0L C30A V6 with VTEC, paired to a crisp 5-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The all-aluminum monocoque chassis remains rigid and true, supported by a double-wishbone suspension with forged aluminum control arms that provide unparalleled tactile feedback. This vehicle is in concours-level condition, showing zero oil seepage, perfect compression numbers, and a pristine cooling system. The exterior retains its original deep luster, while the cockpit is free of leather shrinkage or bolster wear. A rare, mechanically synchronized driving machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
