    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car remains in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or blemishes, while the original alloy wheels are pristine and free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-end infotainment system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has recently undergone a multi-point inspection and full fluid service to ensure it drives as perfectly as it looks. The sale includes both original master keys, all factory manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example.",
